data.description: Simple Living!  This 55+ community might be the perfect spot for you.  This well kept 2 bedroom 1.5 bath condo is centrally located in a nice Alfred, ME association.  The unit is attached to one other via 1 car garage and offers a private setting.  From the covered front porch enter into a large open concept living space.  The unit offers a spacious kitchen,  large dining area, sunny living room.  There is also a bonus 4 season room built off the back.  Master suite w/ bath.  2nd bedroom and 1/2 bath.  The unit offer true single story living with the laundry on the main floor.  The full basement provides ample space for storage or hobbies.  Snow removal and yard maintenance are included as part of the association fee.  Don't miss this amazing opportunity to live in Southern Maine!
